    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine Dei eterni. Anni ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu Chisti
                        millesimo CXLVIII, in die mercurii qui fuit decimus intrante mense marcii,
                        indicione undecima. <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                                ><name ref="Bruningus">Brunichus</name></persName> testar de <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/59">Verona</placeName> investivit
                        domnum <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"><name
                                ref="Andreas">Andream</name></persName> ad proprium, ad <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietatem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Offersio/donatio #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2474">Sancti Zilii</orgName>, nominative de <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals">petia una de terra
                            aratoria</rs> iuris sui, que iacet in <rs key="#Fundi">fundo</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fundi #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Roads" ref="#places/4184"
                            >Gebiti</placeName>, ubi dicitur <placeName
                                key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Roads" ref="#places/4184">Pradelle</placeName>.
                        Habet <rs key="#Size">per longum de uno latere perticas viginti et octo, de
                            alio latere perticas decem et octo et pedes sex, de uno capite perticas
                            quattuordecim, de alio capite perticas novem et pedem unum; et non longe
                            ad eo capite perticas quattuordecim et pedes septem</rs>; de uno latere
                        iura <orgName>Sancti Petri</orgName> iacet, de alio latere <persName><name
                                ref="Grausus">Grauso</name></persName> habet, de ambobus capitibuus
                            <rs key="#Roads">via</rs> percurens. Insuper pro anime sue suorumque
                        parentum remedio, filiis suis adstantibus et consentientibus, obligavit se
                        et suos heredes adversus suprascriptum donnum Andream suisque successoribus
                        suprascriptam terram sicut supra legitur in integrum ab omni homine
                        deffensare, sub pena <rs key="#Penalty">dupli</rs> qualis res fuerit in
                        consimili loco. Actum in Verona. Signum + manus suprascripti Brunichi, qui
                        hanc <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam offercionis</rs> fieri rogavit ad
                        partem suprascripte ecclesie. Signum + <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Bonifacius"
                                >Benefactus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Ingelerius"
                                >Engelerius</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Gandulfus/pistor"
                                >Gandulfus</name></persName> pistor. + Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Iohannes/Baraterius"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, qui Baraterius vocor, rogatus hanc cartulam
                            <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
